{'id': 38801071, 'body': "Hello Tasman, 

We are pleased to learn that the challenges have been motivating for you to continue swimming. We're committed to enhancing this feature, aiming to create even more engaging challenges that can further propel swimmers like you to conquer new milestones. Regarding the slow updates, could you provide us with more details about this issue? Understanding the root cause will help us address it effectively and ensure smoother updates in the future.For additional support, kindly forward your feedback using the support feature located within the mobile app's settings.Your feedback is invaluable as we work towards improving your experience. 
