{'id': 6795612, 'body': 'During September of 2018, we communicated that our support for Pebble users was coming to close (https://blog.swim.com/the-end-of-the-pebble-era/). This change is of significant impact to many of our long time Swim.com users and our own Swim.com team.

As we head into the new year, Pebble users will no longer be able to connect or sync swim workouts to Swim.com. This brings closure to the era of Pebble with Swim.com. The team at Swim.com does not want to leave the many dedicated swimmers who have been with us for many years out of the water. We very much want to keep you as part of the Swim.com community and, more importantly, ensure you can track and monitor your swim performance.

We are offering a special discount for all of our Pebble users. This discount is good toward the purchase of a new device through SwimOutlet.com. If you are interested in taking advantage of this offer, please contact us at support.swim.com.', 'modified': '2019-01-11T18:56:06Z'}
